Text:
1. Don't put them in a .RAR file , cause that will put doubt in many minds , especially since this is your first upload .

2. Give some description of your pictures . Are they porn , are they holiday pictures , are they pictures of your mum knitting , or pictures of your dog fetching a stick .
I got bored waiting on your description , well people it's wallpapers .

When creating torrents in the future, try to come up with a more descriptive torrent posting title of what it is that you are sharing than "my first torrent".
Look at how other, more experienced uploaders do it.
